        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar gender = parseFloat(gender);\nvar time = parseFloat(time);\nvar anomaly = parseFloat(anomaly);\nvar grade = parseFloat(grade);\n\nvar index = gender + time + anomaly + grade;\n\nvar rate;\n\nif (index == 1) {\n    rate = 89;\n} else if (index == 2) {\n    rate = 69;\n} else if (index == 3) {\n    rate = 53;\n} else if (index == 4) {\n    rate = 16;\n} else {\n    rate = 11;\n}\n\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: index,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: rate + '% rate of resolution'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Index',\n    value: index,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'VURx'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Resolution',\n    value: rate,\n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Rate of resolution'\n});",
